197
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:06,040
Not screaming when you're scared so you don't disturb others...

198
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:07,460
Very impressive.

199
00:13:07,460 --> 00:13:09,370
Oh it's Takeru.

200
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:11,750
What are you doing at this hour?

201
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:14,170
You're a kid - go to sleep at 9 and wake up at 6.

202
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:16,020
