204
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,260
What do you mean like mine?!

205
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:22,900
It's sorta your fault.

206
00:13:22,900 --> 00:13:24,110
4 hours ago

207
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:27,050
Hey, have a bottle about this big?

208
00:13:27,050 --> 00:13:29,400
I'm building something.

209
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,090
Here!

210
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:33,650
An energy drink for when you're tired! Napotamin C!

211
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:37,320
But I need an empty bottle...

212
00:13:40,690 --> 00:13:44,750
It had a really strong taste, but I didn't want to waste it so I drank it all.

213
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,720
And now I can't sleep at all.

214
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:52,720
Half a bottle keeps me up, but you drunk it all.

215
00:13:52,990 --> 00:13:56,010
But thanks to that, my castle is complete!

216
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:57,790
