218
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:05,040
Is it okay?! It's not, isn't it? It's not!

219
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:07,640
You're ridiculously happy looking.

220
00:14:08,310 --> 00:14:10,720
Well, it's late night to a kid,

221
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:13,360
