255
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:53,710
Augh. I'll get it out myself.

256
00:15:53,710 --> 00:15:56,370
SS is an abbreviation for slingshot!

257
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:59,250
Like I'd know! Just call it a slingshot, you idiot.

258
